## 🚢 Production Deployment

### Using Docker Compose
```bash
docker-compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up -d
```

### Using Kubernetes
```bash
helm install ad-setup ./charts/ad-setup \
  --namespace active-directory \
  --values values.prod.yaml
```

